---
import rap from '../../assets/images/DrumMixers/rap.png';
import linea from '../../assets/images/RapBins/lineas.png';
---
<section class="w-full mt-20 font-bold">
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-end items-end space-y-2">
        <div class="h-0.5 w-1/3 bg-blueMain"></div>
        <div class="h-0.5 w-1/5 bg-redBg"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-32">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-blueMain text-center">Ranging capacity from 10 to 25 Tph</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full flex gap-10 px-8 md:px-32 mt-20">
        <div class="w-full">
            <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">RAP Collar</h2><br>
            <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
                Built to withstand the abrasive nature of RAP, these feeders are constructed with high-strength materials that reduce wear 
                and extend service life. Their calibrated design ensures that RAP enters the drum mixer's collar at the optimal rate, preventing 
                surges or blockages that could affect mixing efficiency. This precise feeding mechanism helps maintain consistent asphalt quality
                 while optimizing fuel and material consumption.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
            <img src={rap.src} alt="" class="w-1/2">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-32">
        <img src="" alt="">
    </div>
    <div>
        <img src="" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="w-full md:pl-32 font-thin text-base md:text-lg flex flex-col gap-6">
            <p>
                Equipped with large-capacity RAP bins, Triaso® RAP Feeders accommodate high-volume material loads
                 while ensuring even distribution. The system is designed to prevent material buildup, ensuring a steady and 
                 uniform flow into the drum mixer without disruptions.
            </p>
            <div class="w-full flex flex-col justify-start items-start space-y-2">
                <div class="h-0.5 w-1/3 bg-redBg"></div>
                <div class="h-0.5 w-1/3 bg-blueMain ml-10"></div>
            </div>
            <p>
                By incorporating Triaso® RAP Feeders, asphalt plants can enhance RAP utilization, improve mix consistency, 
                and support sustainable production by efficiently reintegrating recycled materials into the asphalt mix.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-white bg-blueMain rounded-2xl">
            <div class="p-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl">Available in 10 or 25-ton capacity bins</h2><br>
                <p class="font-thin text-lg md:text-xl">With configurations of one, two, or three RAP bin units</p>
            </div>
            <img src={linea.src} alt="">
        </div>
    </div>

</section>